| Question or Issue                                           | Answer / response                                                                                                                                             |
|-------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Warning about "cli out of date, is already loaded"?         | So far, the best option is to terminate the RStudio session and re-open a new one and start from scratch again.                                               |
| How do I see how others are coding in R for their projects? | Go to the [`ukbiobank-team` repository list](https://github.com/orgs/steno-aarhus/teams/ukbiobank-team/repositories) on the Steno Aarhus GitHub organization. |
